{"tid":1996864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陶輝私竇】《蘋果》踢爆違法 民政總署證無旅館牌：有證據將檢控","createTime":"2020-05-01T08:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T12:49:22.000Z","uid":7363,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bca0224f37cc77314e8bf94c329cd40bb0357c63","tid":1996864,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》踢爆警務處助理處長陶輝及妻子，將一間清水灣牌照屋包裝成民宿出租，涉嫌無牌經營旅館。民政事務總署證實，該單位並無領取牌照，署方轄下的牌照處將會跟進，若有足夠證據會作出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n陶輝及同為警員的妻子張雅詩，過去6年將碧水新村61A號的牌照屋包裝為民宿出租，並在facebook群組多番發帖宣傳，民宿的租期可以短至三日兩夜，每年總收入可達31萬元。二人的舉動不但涉違反牌照屋條款，更可能涉及無牌經營旅館。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署最新回覆《蘋果》指，除非有關處所內提供的所有住宿，每次出租期均為連續28天或以上，否則就必須遵守《旅館業條例》的規限。根據《條例》，「旅館」是指任何處所，其佔用人、東主或租客顯示在他可提供的住宿範圍內，會向到臨該處所的人士提供收費的住宿地方。牌照處在接獲任何懷疑無牌經營旅館的舉報後，會在8個工作天內進行巡查。<br />\n<br />\n民政署證實，碧水新村61A號未有領取旅館牌照，牌照處將會作出跟進，如有足夠證據證明相關處所涉及無牌經營旅館，便會採取檢控行動。翻查資料，根據《條例》，經營或管理無牌旅館均屬刑事罪行，一經定罪會留有案底，最高可被處罰款20萬元及監禁兩年。警方至今拒絕正面回應。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果牙膏 必屬佳品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7791fc344cd149b8177e88bc17062e912e14cbfd","tid":1996864,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:54:13.000Z","msg":"有排擠了"},{"pid":"5e916cb24779f13c19782d6ab163a4cc2c274a15","tid":1996864,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"condom"},{"pid":"90bf8ffd5f534cede615ea53048f635225e97bb6","tid":1996864,"uid":68463,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"搵唔到證據 見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5ce5edbeef73bd73229a3ad7f8e3bf89b00112","tid":1996864,"uid":271516,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSx5uuf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSx5uuf.gif&h=b9c498ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9996680355a228009a8a99671608d309bfefaf5","tid":1996864,"uid":77187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"呢區最大係我 邊個夠膽檢控我?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d35a32bd6a5e36319c05d959f3fed4793422f0","tid":1996864,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:48:05.000Z","msg":"鄧小強出黎咪。等你出黎講歪理"},{"pid":"3113c3c47ecee2a4f343305bb70f6082fdfe1eaf","tid":1996864,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"等睇陶輝變condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e13fff65096bee11f7747e0d5b23956877b90f","tid":1996864,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946f1bbbaa070ec15d574fca0531134188cac7e1","tid":1996864,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"今晚7點半就係沙田新城市和你唱 <br />\n幫手推上去thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「行動」51新城市和你唱 沙田柚搖滾準備好未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1996446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1996446</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4b478c0edaf722088e64a432094c63d1f787646","tid":1996864,"uid":180293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"轉頭未又係笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbb75e0731b8a9971160088c36de24cd629df73","tid":1996864,"uid":44980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass